{"tid":2050734,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"學術討論 香港人應否繼續悼念64","createTime":"2020-06-04T09:59:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-04T10:23:15.000Z","uid":309822,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8dd97300f9df6ba94c81f75a127f9ca9cdbb1f20","tid":2050734,"uid":309822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T09:59:47.000Z","msg":"純學術討論 非五毛分化<br />\n<br />\n香港人想獨立 摒棄中國人嘅身份 但又走去平反六四 係咪好矛盾？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果你係話去六四集會係想反共 但又點解唔搞埋悼念東歐革命個d反共革命（波蘭工會/捷克布拉格之春）<br />\n<br />\n係咪始終摒棄唔到中國人身份？"},{"pid":"4008445155b96b8a170a82edb18a0af4d78e0efb","tid":2050734,"uid":309822,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:02:18.000Z","msg":"如果係想令人繼續知8964真相 大可以係教育 宣傳等方面去做 <br />\n<br />\n正如外國人係人都知64真相 都唔會搞悼念集會"},{"pid":"3061cb9f3eb169a7cc4ec7579398b2e03c57dfa2","tid":2050734,"uid":309822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:02:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d23c3e99527c098c22ec50550b0f9d11c828cb81","tid":2050734,"uid":309822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:02:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ab5748e65f1717c224e8f93f186fde89ccfe6570","tid":2050734,"uid":309822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:02:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fc0b66c343353889122d9340da0fddc6cbbbb40e","tid":2050734,"uid":309822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6b14846402c6c9a5f0f977f48465197af29d1549","tid":2050734,"uid":309822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:03:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bc080ddbaababd4b38e1c60e69821f0e2f2f7e21","tid":2050734,"uid":309822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:03:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5cf0e69ef456bf5397c4c5ae8d4e9421275c2262","tid":2050734,"uid":309822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-04T10:04:14.000